    <h3><a href="/halfgirlfriend">HALF GIRLFRIEND - BY CHETAN BHAGAT</a></h3>
    <p id="para">Half Girlfriend is the much-awaited novel by the famous Indian novelist, Chetan Bhagat. It delves into new and different dimensions that relationships have in today’s world. Half Girlfriend is a story of Bihari boy Madhav, a Hindi speaking Bihari who falls in love with Riya, an influential Delhi girl on the campus of prestigious St. Stephen's College. Madhav belongs to middle class family, while Riya is from higher class and both have different lifestyles.</p>
